        "name": "Venomous Bite (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Bone Spider lunges at a target, attempting to sink its razor-sharp fangs into their flesh to deal D4 Piercing damage on a hit. If the attack hits, the target must succeed on an Endurance check or be Paralyzed for 1 round.</p></div>"
