        "name": "Skittering Assault (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Bone Spider swiftly moves across the battlefield, scaling walls and terrain with unnatural agility and attacking, dealing D6 Slashing damage. If the attack hits, the target must succeed on a Dodge check or be knocked Prone.</p></div>"
