    "description": "<div><p>The skeletal form of Bone Spiders is an amalgamation of bones from various creatures, woven together with dark magic into a twisted, eight-legged horror. The Bone Spider's razor-sharp fangs, fashioned from the remnants of long-dead predators, drip with venom that can induce both paralysis and excruciating pain. These abominations move with uncanny silence, able to scale walls and ceilings with unnatural agility, making them elusive and relentless predators.</p></div>",
